This paper discusses the integration of vision and language in AI, which is a topic that falls under multiple sub-categories in arXiv CS. The most likely sub-categories are cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as they directly relate to the paper's focus on language and image/video analysis. The paper also discusses the use of corpora and quality metrics, which are topics that fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper's analysis of datasets could also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves categorizing and evaluating large amounts of data.
